trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientEnumerator"></xref> class provides enumeration functionality for the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientCollection"></xref> collection.

The <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientEnumerator.Current"></xref> property retrieves the current <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipient"></xref> object from the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientCollection"></xref> collection.

A <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipient"></xref> object that represents the current recipient in the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientCollection"></xref> collection.

The <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientEnumerator.MoveNext"></xref> method advances the enumeration to the next <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipient"></xref> object in the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientCollection"></xref> collection.

`true` if the enumeration successfully moved to the next <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipient"></xref> object; `false` if the enumeration moved past the last item in the enumeration.

The <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientEnumerator.Reset"></xref> method resets the enumeration to the first <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipient"></xref> object in the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientCollection"></xref> collection.

The <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientEnumerator.System#Collections#IEnumerator#Current"></xref> property retrieves the current <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipient"></xref> object from the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientCollection"></xref> collection.

A <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipient"></xref> object that represents the current recipient in the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientCollection"></xref> collection.
